        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1888-01-11T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1888-01-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="273" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d273">
                <head>No. 273.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bayard</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Maury</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1888-01-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">January</hi> 11, 1888</date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 54.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>,: I transmit for your information a copy<note n="*" xml:id="d273fn1">For inclosure, Mr. Roberts to Mr. Bayard, November
                        11, 1887, No. 166, see Document No. 131, <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_178">p. 178</ref>.</note> of a dispatch from our minister in
                    Chili relative to the re-appearance of the cholera at Santiago, and intimating
                    that the quarantine measures at Panama are too rigid.</p>
                <p>Special instructions are withheld for the present, but you will take such
                    opportunities as in your judgment seem to be proper to deprecate any greater
                    restriction of transit facilities than are demanded by sanitary
                    considerations.</p>
                <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">T. F. Bayard.</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
